  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-11d6321c-1895-49db-8cac-16dd62271c8a\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1fdb591f-55e3-41a2-a561-48947a796e03\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-fb5e26be-fbed-4720-8d9c-58c836e7e0bf\"><b>안녕하세요! 몸과 마음을 건강하게</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c29cbb57-856d-45e2-83f0-ff7a8cd6950e\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffef34;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-91b1458e-04b5-48cd-b574-bd0c78c1758a\"><b>이수한의원</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-62fc3c8b-82b0-40f8-8c8b-a48d7e11acbd\"><b>입니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-11d6321c-1895-49db-8cac-16dd62271c8a\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-sticker se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6c8d17a6-4216-42b2-b310-d45743f13f12\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-sticker se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-sticker\">\n                                <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" class=\"__se_sticker_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"sticker\" data-linkdata='{\"src\" : \"\", \"packCode\" : \"motion2d_01\", \"seq\" : \"6\", \"width\" : \"\", \"height\" : \"\"}'>\n                                    <img src=\"https://storep-phinf.pstatic.net/motion2d_01/original_6.png?type=p100_100\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-sticker-image\" />\n                                </a>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-90993b46-41dc-4df3-ab1e-1777832bf061\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2fd1eba5-ddd5-4891-b150-dfdaaf677fa6\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-e413ecf7-9a42-4de6-9a2b-de1d746f2a64\">변비는 많은 사람들이 겪는 흔한 증상이지만, 소양인에게는 특별히 더 주의해야 할 ‘체질의 경고’가 될 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-90993b46-41dc-4df3-ab1e-1777832bf061\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-7fd6b036-3ba9-4a56-91bf-00996cb10812\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-center\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-35818763-2234-4ea9-8c20-dc8698d1cee3\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-35818763-2234-4ea9-8c20-dc8698d1cee3\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/fcf97461a59ac7e9.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1400\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1400\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/fcf97461a59ac7e9.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/fcf97461a59ac7e9.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"500\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-35818763-2234-4ea9-8c20-dc8698d1cee3\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3f749b02-8725-426b-8870-9f1ec07be11d\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-698fb0ed-c667-427f-9ac9-b064b5fa8928\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-27caf03e-a27a-4815-ab1b-fc88384675e2\"><b>✔ 소양인과 변비의 관계</b></span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0e8054eb-90bb-497d-948c-efd2114a6bbf\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-d823b96d-7c28-45fc-8d80-2499c97bb42a\">소양인은 한의학적으로 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-bea7970d-1c3d-4a66-9dd7-134a9fc6d3e1\"><b>비위(脾胃)는 강한 편이지만, </b></span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0521535d-3c57-46ec-a7b8-31035b075bc8\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-62896a3d-925a-416a-a639-6c6ea123de4b\"><b>신장과 대장 기능은 약한 체질</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-899506af-24be-4827-898a-ea3628c1d73e\">로 알려져 있습니다.</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-be1629e3-30dd-42e5-8a99-5c9ab5fdd0e5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-e114df7d-3b42-41cb-a384-6bf0490df28b\">즉, </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-ef7b9bbf-5342-4b50-9032-804af71cdf05\"><b>상체는 열이 많고 하체는 약한 상열하한 체질</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-81755459-5a8b-4420-94d7-9f659fedddb5\">로, </span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-85fe686b-e94b-44c3-9e9d-2d60cab3037e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-cce4726f-64c3-4881-88bc-bd11b0679f7f\">대장 기능이 쉽게 영향을 받습니다.</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-66065d72-bca1-4389-b35d-e18c0c15bed5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-0a09d36e-05d8-4f39-8b43-172a35dd7aa1\">특히 다음과 같은 생활습관이나 체질 특성이 소양인 변비를 악화시킬 수 있습니다:</span></p><ul class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-bullet-disc\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9551f748-d2b8-473f-8bb2-d16c6d11759b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-dbe597cb-9f35-4ce0-a1b5-3fb7659d212a\">열이 위로 몰리면서 장이 건조해짐</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-42f620b8-f000-464e-bedd-e6d019adf37e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-ee0c78b7-e980-4467-9114-f1a9fc51a459\">매운 음식, 고기 섭취를 좋아함</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c06727cc-35e9-4177-ad08-78a2b3fbd882\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-87a682fc-c182-43fc-8af5-1cd9f954f0ab\">긴장감이 많고, 스트레스를 받으면 위로 열이 더 오름</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-cec3fd3a-705c-4b7e-85bd-4c515730e69a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-9003fc5a-615c-456a-80d3-462ac6d23cf1\">수분 섭취가 부족한 편</span></p></li></ul><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9fc54b6d-b808-4721-8c31-db5bd0e57fbf\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-b1bfeedf-0a70-45b9-aca4-4e05fc938f55\">이러한 요인들은 단순한 일시적 변비를 넘어, </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-d0204141-c46d-4a85-876f-951e4ec2eafd\"><b>체내 순환 불균형</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-0c0fd891-534b-4cc2-aba4-4193e27e0bed\">을 나타내는 중요한 신호가 될 수 있습니다.</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a3974ec0-108f-4fa4-b41b-072c6706377a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-27e79253-c8ac-4077-9b8d-0dbfd184fd0c\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1e80fd58-3d00-4e82-95db-0b7c058aaf73\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-e57705a9-1eab-44fd-a186-36754b795561\"><b>✔ 이런 증상이 있다면 </b></span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-16c58b79-18bb-498e-aa86-5f3c819942f8\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-79e64dca-da0b-4e35-a0f6-74ade198bc20\"><b>소양인 변비일 수 있습니다</b></span></p><ul class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-bullet-disc\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2e216f5b-1621-43a3-8b2a-257b805c0f63\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-9c7d5733-7511-4e06-b9a2-1b22f28f520c\">배에 가스가 차고 더부룩함</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c29a6c12-ff18-4b45-a971-f62a55e40e71\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-54d61184-aa40-41f3-8a84-2cbfe07472f4\">대변이 굵고 단단하거나, 너무 묽게 나옴</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-267bdba1-71ca-49be-bccf-2e54fdaf69c8\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-a39cf1f0-8f5b-4f9e-9ea0-14ca1cf962e5\">배변 시 힘을 많이 줘야 하고 불쾌감이 큼</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d7b4b10c-dcab-4777-8094-e213a4a35c76\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-026fe7e0-99db-4806-9a14-0577a21186f9\">대변을 보고도 잔변감이 있음</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-587976cf-d251-4de6-8e6c-09deef126f24\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-f3989df0-151e-4bb4-b704-193def197ece\">피부 트러블, 구취, 피로감 동반</span></p></li></ul><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-3f749b02-8725-426b-8870-9f1ec07be11d\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3a9162c9-de74-4613-9312-af1d4a7fcdec\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-3a9162c9-de74-4613-9312-af1d4a7fcdec\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/4a79a2650a03bf82.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1536\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1024\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/4a79a2650a03bf82.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/4a79a2650a03bf82.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"333\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-3a9162c9-de74-4613-9312-af1d4a7fcdec\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-47a54507-f59e-47c9-99b7-4a9ee2f65630\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e106ba06-cccb-4798-84a8-882011a8645f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-7b4c17d5-09d5-4082-b48f-351156724bf3\"><b>✔ 한의학적 치료 접근</b></span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b5b15b81-320c-402a-99c8-4bbc51add118\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-c1a25984-64ca-48fe-a7f1-8ee676620bf7\">소양인 변비는 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-ae121415-673e-42a9-91db-c122ee053ff6\"><b>대장 열을 식히고 장의 진액을 보충해주는 방향</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-cd18ca5e-4cba-407b-8f5d-52d3859f9c0f\">으로 치료합니다.</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-29f1a494-c3e4-4ea9-bae1-a57798765c46\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-e1e0a79a-a916-46b5-94b8-ddf52ae32ecb\">대표적인 한약 및 처방은 다음과 같습니다:</span></p><ul class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-bullet-disc\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1ea43d04-d0e4-4b45-b57b-b2e81ef131a3\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-fc2227c0-5649-47ca-b382-c9ca7efb1b34\"><b>양격산화탕(凉膈散火湯)</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-0a126389-c4f0-4929-9754-642cd59e9591\">: 위와 장의 열을 내려주고 건조함 개선</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9a2a6f04-5ece-4ae2-90e4-94961beae643\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-4f8347fd-ffe7-41ea-97c1-9d86a5b92a02\"><b>도핵승기탕(桃核承氣湯)</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-f35e1a0e-6d60-45da-9642-6f0ceec83f12\">: 장의 정체된 기운을 풀어주고 배변 원활</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-24020679-1f17-47fe-b46b-61347d63d90d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-9d6e9edd-52ed-49dc-a1a8-1522a151eaab\"><b>윤장환(潤腸丸)</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-c29c6a25-e59e-4ae3-8cae-0f39c082d39a\">: 장을 부드럽게 하고 진액 보충</span></p></li></ul><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8eed83b6-e25d-4b43-ace1-d3150ed1428e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-32265c76-fdf2-4ba3-8137-6cc179b5d8fa\">또한 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-43024740-c0ce-4677-9b0b-13e2621f1649\"><b>침, 뜸, 복부 마사지, 뜸 치료 등으로 하초 기능을 강화</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-4d35b9e9-e8f9-4ba5-a82f-8afa7cfb6bad\">하고, 장의 운동성을 회복시키는 방법도 병행합니다.</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-016d2b5c-e556-460e-9406-f85a75279bba\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-561e6818-0847-45ee-964c-182687c0f705\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6e1097f1-c071-4a2c-a32b-226624dbd847\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-66873b8e-2c50-4749-87fc-b74196493539\"><b>✔ 생활 속 관리법</b></span></p><ul class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-bullet-disc\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0c20a529-a090-4886-a238-6d766a036bfa\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-2a2ca407-ce36-469e-9b74-771a7cd2af2f\">충분한 수분 섭취 (하루 1.5~2리터 이상)</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-26009502-a3c3-48f5-94d6-706bb349b457\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-2d3892b0-d202-42a4-aa8d-cefccc4e2142\">채소, 과일 등 섬유질이 풍부한 식사</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-17952a99-3588-4389-bffb-726761bb3985\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-8bbc8f31-fce7-4ed1-ab23-2c9ea68f2b21\">아침 공복에 따뜻한 물 한 컵</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8a5916ab-c09b-4f9d-9968-ca22e8fbc37d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-8fd41bcd-a711-4082-a6ab-6731ff37f425\">과로 피하고 수면 충분히</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-478d02ef-58e1-4c72-a52d-ed785cb3cb45\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-b90b3a4d-451f-4382-97d6-0344ffb99fe9\">냉한 음식, 매운 음식 줄이기</span></p></li></ul><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ebedc622-d17d-494a-945b-2e86c0efb1fe\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-e3379efd-ff52-4da1-88d9-b253d134d085\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-47a54507-f59e-47c9-99b7-4a9ee2f65630\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-video se-l-default\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-video se-section-align-center se-l-default\" >\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-video\" id=\"SE-23b2edee-9085-499d-a14b-e11d2ddfb1f7\">\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module='{\"type\":\"v2_video\", \"id\" :\"SE-23b2edee-9085-499d-a14b-e11d2ddfb1f7\", \"data\" : { \"videoType\" : \"player\", \"vid\" : \"624DA032500EBCDA184BDA2B8AF